10#include "ipf.h"
11
12int geticmptype(family, name)
13 int family;
14 char *name;
15{
16 icmptype_t *i;
17
18 for (i = icmptypelist; i->it_name != NULL; i++) {
19 if (!strcmp(name, i->it_name)) {
20 if (family == AF_INET)
21 return i->it_v4;
22#ifdef USE_INET6
23 if (family == AF_INET6)
24 return i->it_v6;
25#endif
26 return -1;
27 }
28 }
29
30 return -1;
31}
